// Copy to `ios/Flutter/DartDefines.xcconfig` (gitignored) to inject custom
// `--dart-define` values when building from Xcode.
//
// Recommended: generate this file via `bash tool/gen_dart_defines_xcconfig.sh`.
//
// Example (NOT real keys):
// DART_DEFINES = $(inherited),<base64(KEY=VALUE)>,<base64(KEY=VALUE)>

